            <h2>Data Security</h2>
            
            <p>We implement comprehensive security measures to protect your personal information:</p>

            <h3>Technical Safeguards</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Encryption:</strong> Data transmission and storage using industry-standard encryption</li>
                <li><strong>Access Controls:</strong> Restricted access to personal information on a need-to-know basis</li>
                <li><strong>Secure Servers:</strong> Protected hosting environment with regular security updates</li>
                <li><strong>Firewalls:</strong> Network security measures to prevent unauthorized access</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Administrative Safeguards</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Staff Training:</strong> Regular privacy and security training for all personnel</li>
                <li><strong>Access Management:</strong> Regular review and monitoring of data access privileges</li>
                <li><strong>Incident Response:</strong> Established procedures for handling security incidents</li>
                <li><strong>Regular Audits:</strong> Periodic security assessments and compliance reviews</li>
            </ul>

            <!-- Data Retention -->
            <h2>Data Retention</h2>
            
            <p>We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to:</p>
            <ul>
